                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;For the behavior of Visual Studio, please check: &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cpp/preprocessor/hash-include-directive-c-cpp?view=vs-2019&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cpp/preprocessor/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

