            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@piCookie both &amp;lt;filename&amp;gt; and &quot;filename&quot; search for implementation-defined places. So what is the difference ?&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/1418457/onmyway133&quot; title=&quot;43,053 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;onmyway133&lt;/a&gt;
