                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment71681358_50266&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2017-02-15 23:14:52Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Feb 15, 2017 at 23:14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;What is exact source of the text? Is it from normative part of IEEE Std 1003.1, 2013?&lt;/span&gt;

