            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;This was my first thought too. The manpage for gcc includes this as do others. There&apos;s also a similar thing for libraries - &lt;code&gt;-L&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
